name: /about/team/ceo
content:
Mr. Gandalf - CEO
With decades of experience in the magical realm, Mr. Gandalf is a visionary leader. He's guided MagicWand Co. to new heights.
Email: gandalf.ceo@magicwand.co
Quote: 'Magic is not just in wands, it's within us.'

name: /about/team/head_engineering
content:
Ms. Hermione - Head of Engineering
Ms. Hermione is at the forefront of magical technology. Her innovations have revolutionized how we interact with magic.
Email: hermione.engineering@magicwand.co
Achievements: Creator of the Self-Replenishing Spellbook
Interests: Combining ancient spells with modern tech

name: /about/team/chief_potion_master
content:

A master of potions, Dr. Snape's expertise lies in creating the most effective and intricate brews.
Email: snape.potions@magicwand.co
Famous Creation: The Everlasting Elixir
Philosophy: 'In every potion, there is a story.'
